Package com.rift.coad.rdf.semantic

Interface Summary
Query This interface defines the semantic query interface.
Resource This is the resource interface for the coadunation semantic library.
Session This object represents a session object.
SessionManager This class is responsible for managing the semantic connections and information.
SPARQLQuery This object represents the SPARQL query object.
SPARQLResultRow This interface represents an sql result set row.
Transaction This interface defines the transaction interface provided by the semantic objects.
 

Class Summary
Constants This class defines all the constants
PluginConstants The plugin constants used by this object.
RDFConstants This file contains a bunch of RDF constants
RDFFormats The RDF formats.
SessionManagerBuilder This object is responsible for instantiating the session manager.
 

Exception Summary
QueryException The query exception thrown when there is an exception with the query interfaces.
ResourceException This exception is thrown when there is an error with the resource object.
SemanticException This exception is thrown when there is a problem with the semantic libraries.
SessionException This object is thrown when there is an exception with the sessioning managed by the semenatic library.
TransactionException This exception is thrown when there is an error with the transaction manager.
